Spaced repetition (in-app practice)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In-app review scheduling uses the FSRS-5 algorithm, ported into this app from
open-spaced-repetition/swift-fsrs (MIT License) — re-implemented in
WordOfTheDay/Features/Practice/ReviewEngine.swift, not linked as a dependency. It
runs entirely on-device; no review data leaves the phone. Anki's own AGPL code is
never used; the Anki export is plain CSV that Anki imports natively.
  https://github.com/open-spaced-repetition/swift-fsrs
